description: Samhällsbyggnadsbolaget i Norden AB operates as a real estate company. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 14 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2014-11-12. The company cooperates with municipalities and other tenants on a long-term basis. The firm operates Offentlige Bygg AS as subsidiary.
name: Samhallsbyggnadsbolaget I Norden AB
